Turn to this focused collection of the most relevant orthopaedic trauma lectures from several past AAOS Annual Meetings, presented by orthopaedic surgeons who specialize in trauma.

Doctors Ricci and Tornetta selected topics that give you experience-based solutions and powerful insights on how trauma experts solve a number of their toughest cases. Some of today's leading trauma surgeons draw on their own experience to guide you through this volume. Their section introductions and commentary relates these practical topics and hands-on surgical solutions to your everyday clinical practice.
